# Azure Data Engineering Projects

## 📊 Customer 360 Sales Pipeline

An end-to-end ETL pipeline built with Azure Data Factory that combines daily sales from three sources (online, stores, app) into a single aggregated view for reporting.

### 🏗️ Architecture
- **Source**: CSV files in Azure Blob Storage
- **Validation**: Get Metadata + If Condition to verify file existence
- **Transformations**: Data Flow with Union, Derived Column, Filter, Aggregate
- **Destination**: Azure SQL Database

### 🔧 Key Features
- ✅ Dynamic parameters for date-based processing
- ✅ File validation before processing
- ✅ Source tracking (Online/Stores/App)
- ✅ Data cleansing (remove invalid records)
- ✅ Aggregated reporting by category
- ✅ Git-integrated CI/CD ready

### 📈 Sample Output
| Category | TotalAmount | OrderCount | SourceCount |
|----------|-------------|------------|-------------|
| Electronics | 1892.97 | 8 | 3 |
| Furniture | 539.99 | 2 | 1 |
| Media | 44.98 | 2 | 2 |
| Stationery | 38.49 | 2 | 1 |

### 🚀 How to Deploy
1. Clone this repository
2. Deploy ARM template to your Azure subscription
3. Configure linked services with your credentials
4. Trigger the pipeline

